- Why English spelling is inconsistent (historical reasons briefly: Great Vowel Shift, borrowed words)

**RP vs General American key differences:**
| Sound | RP (British) | GenAm (American) | Example |
/ɑː/ pre-nasal | /ɑː/ | /æ/ | dance, path, bath
